{"tid":2331868,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【詭異喪禮】29歲男子死後被製成標本參加自己喪禮　親友驚見死者坐在教堂門口","createTime":"2020-12-19T06:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T08:29:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c039a898b614b571daddd220f637f6a97f9b95a2","tid":2331868,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"加勒比海國家千里達（Trinidad and Tobago）近日進行了一場詭異喪禮，一名男子死後未有被放入棺材，而是被製成標本，穿戴整齊地被送到教堂參加自己的喪禮，惟遭教堂人員拒絕入場，家屬只能將標本放在門口，不少參加喪禮的親友都未認出死者。<br />\n<br />\n29歲的Che Lewis和54歲的父親Adlay Lewis於11月在家中被槍殺。Che死後，友人將其遺體進行防腐處理後，為他穿上粉色西裝、白色西褲、白皮鞋及墨鏡，並將他安放在靈車的後座，一路以坐著的姿勢前往教堂，參加自己的喪禮，而靈車駕駛期間，亦相當受注目。<br />\n<br />\n當遺體被運抵教堂時，教堂人員大吃一驚，並拒絕讓死者入場，親友唯有將遺體安放在椅子上，讓他坐在教堂門口，並於旁邊擺放一張他的生前照片。結果，許多出席喪禮的親友未能認出遺體就是Che本人，紛紛以為是其他前來弔唁的親友，甚至怪責他不戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n負責這場詭異喪禮的殯葬公司老闆表示，這是家屬要求的，以前亦進行過類似喪禮，所以對於這種要求見怪不怪。不過，當地警方認為此舉魯莽，將展開調查，殯葬公司恐被罰款。而當地天主教神父亦批評這種行為不尊重死者，建議教區在葬禮前，要求對方提供所有細節。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2833030/specimen_thumb_20201219_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2833030%2Fspecimen_thumb_20201219_S_1024.jpg&h=c7b5b08e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2833030/001_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2833030%2F001_1024.jpeg&h=c5af3927&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2833030/003_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2833030%2F003_1024.jpeg&h=24c1fd8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2830000/2833030/004_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2830000%2F2833030%2F004_1024.jpeg&h=410c574a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31be39964b978cc012736e85df9ffc8f438c2d01","tid":2331868,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805f549a52fa22bc9d37dc351518df1d220a8e91","tid":2331868,"uid":160592,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"穢土轉生"},{"pid":"ea0c1901d393914feff4321942a4b6507115911c","tid":2331868,"uid":41368,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"不少參加喪禮的親友都未認出死者"},{"pid":"7529b193cef184a292039cc1007c7e0afe7d7430","tid":2331868,"uid":201604,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"照死者意願做 都叫不尊重死者 耶撚真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72e9a329c93500240e12aca782e351c735915dc","tid":2331868,"uid":213656,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:58:14.000Z","msg":"恐怖蠟像館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cdb9930cae22b94654f0bff3cc386a5a336cfc","tid":2331868,"uid":212996,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"其實幾型"},{"pid":"2879529b7eca20b9596143bbed3dcd4ef692c479","tid":2331868,"uid":2267,"like":4,"disl